<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-14 02:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9728 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-NHLNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      03-14 2211
