 &HT;    NEWS FOR KIDS: Captain Underpants to the rescue
 &HT;    By Julie Bookman
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   You can't find anything fun to read? Author Dav Pilkey comes to
the rescue! ``Captain Underpants and the Attack of the Talking
Toilets'' (Blue Sky/Scholastic, $16.95) continues the wacky
adventures of George and Harold, the pals at Horwitz Elementary who
created the goofball superhero. This time a science contest goes
haywire when toilets turn nasty _ and come to life. And don't think
the boys are done with that evil Mr. Krupp!
</P>
