<P>
   DIGITAL-COMMERCE (Undated) _ Whether or not shareholders
ultimately bless or curse the proposed merger of Lycos with Barry
Diller's television shopping company, USA Networks, the deal may
well have catalyzed a long-overdue rethinking of the business of
Internet portals, those launching pads from which millions of Web
surfers rocket onto the Internet each day. By Denise Caruso.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 7 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   PATENTS (Undated) _ Women inventors; sandal socks. By Sabra
Chartrand.
