<HEADLINE>
STUDY SAYS EARLY SOCIAL INTERACTION AVERTS RISKY TEEN-AGE
BEHAVIOR 
</HEADLINE>
  (ms) 
 By JANE E. BRODY   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
