444-8286.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
GOODYKOONTZ-COLUMN (Undated) _ How word was spread of Caesar's
murder to the rest of the world back in 44 B.C. isn't known. But if
the murder took place today, it's easy to imagine the media
firestorm. By BILL GOODYKOONTZ. Story will move in the ``L''
