WBA and IBF heavyweight champion Evander Holyfield into the ropes
Saturday night at Madison Square Garden. The long-awaited fight
between Holyfield and Lewis ended in a draw after 12 rounds on
Saturday despite a widespread belief from reporters and boxing fans
alike that Lewis was the true winner of the bout. (G. Paul
Burnett/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
